        public void write(ColumnVector columnVector,

                  int batchRows)
        Write all data of a ColumnVector.
        Parameters:
        columnVector - Which holds the paimon data.
        pickedInColumn - Which rows is picked to write. Pick all if null. This is used to adapt deletion vector.
        startIndex - From where to start writing.
        batchRows - How many rows to write.
